  "summary": "This final chunk of Kieckhefer’s *Forbidden Rites* study includes index entries and brief references to ritual elements in the Munich Handbook (CLM 849), especially focusing on named spirits (demons and angels), ritual implements (circles, swords, mirrors), ingredients (candles, hoopoes), and textual sources. It also lists specific folios with diagrams: seals for planets/days of the week (fols. 73r–74v), Seal of Solomon (fol. 95v), tripartite prayer circles (fols. 99v, 103r), Trinitarian concentric bands (fol. 105v), and a complex character (fol. 108r).",
